headline: Linde Announces Major U.S. Investments to Support Commercial Space Sector
summary: WOKING, England, July 21, 2025--Linde (Nasdaq: LIN) today announced ambitious new investments to fuel the next frontier of space exploration. With two new long-term agreements to supply bulk industrial gases for rocket launches, Linde is strengthening its leadership in the rapidly expanding U.S. space industry.
